  m_Name: Samurai - Max Trust
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  data:
    convoName: Samurai - Max Trust
    lines:
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'Orion, I want to speak with you. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Yes? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'I want you to know I appreciate your inclusion of me on this journey.
        I am glad to have been able to work side by side with you to stop Noboru,
        and begin to bring honor back to my clan. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'You fight hard for them. Even with all of the harm they caused, you
        are still loyal. If I were in your place, I would have sworn them off long
        ago. Your devotion is something to be admired, Akihito.  '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: "It is the differences between people that make them special. Without
        them, we would be nothing. In my travels, the people I have disagreed with
        have always taught me the most\u2026 even if my anger sometimes meant they
        did not live long enough to fully teach me\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'I thought your master trained you to control your emotions. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'I was young, and the world was still not fully clear to me. Even now,
        I understand it best when delivering justice in the ways I know how. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'If you were not a samurai, you would make a great philosopher. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'My passion is of a more physical form, but it is true that I am committed
        to my ideology.  '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: 'I trust our fight will continue? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Do the corrupt deserve their penance? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Akihito
      expression: 
      line: Yes. Yes they do.
      audio: {fileID: 0}
